    <body>
        <p>Adair County, Kentucky, resident and stock trader. Adair County, Kentucky, native. Son of Robert Lyon and Catherine G. Lyon. Married to Mary F. &quot;Fannie&quot; Jones Lyon in Adair County on June 5, 1860. Resident of Adair County in 1850. Stock trader in Adair County in 1863.</p>

